snippet.title: Royal Order - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Our medieval fantasy stats-raiser, and Royal Alchemist's indirect sequel is on Kickstarter in November 2021!


Kickstarter ➡️ https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/niftyvisuals/royal-order-a-lgbt-visual-novel


The first demo is already available on both Steam and Itchio. Check us out!


Itchio ➡️ https://nifty-visuals.itch.io/royal-order
Steam ➡️ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1749010/Royal_Order/


Twitter: https://twitter.com/Nifty_Visuals
Tumblr: http://niftyvisuals.tumblr.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/NiftyVisualsVN
